      "default": "ACTIVE_FILTER_UNSPECIFIED",
      "description": "ActiveFilter represents filter options for is_active field.\n\n - ACTIVE_FILTER_UNSPECIFIED: Show all records regardless of active status (default).\n - ACTIVE_FILTER_ACTIVE: Show only active records.\n - ACTIVE_FILTER_INACTIVE: Show only inactive records."
