      "default": "FORMULA_TYPE_UNSPECIFIED",
      "description": "FormulaType represents the type of a formula expression.\n\n - FORMULA_TYPE_UNSPECIFIED: Default unspecified value - used as \"no filter\" in list/export requests.\n - FORMULA_TYPE_CALCULATION: Mathematical calculation using parameter codes (e.g., \"ELEC_CONSUMPTION * ELEC_RATE\").\n - FORMULA_TYPE_SQL_QUERY: SQL query to fetch data from other tables.\n - FORMULA_TYPE_CONSTANT: Constant value (no calculation)."
